%%{init: {"theme": "base", "themeVariables": {"fontSize": "14px"}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as task-solver
    participant D as Host Docker daemon
    participant P as In-proc proxy
    participant B as Sandbox (agent)
    participant U as LLM upstream

    S->>S: Pick job (task + agent bundle)
    S->>S: Clone repo @ parent_sha,<br/>scrub git creds, assemble /work tree
    S->>D: Ensure internal network 'tau-sandbox-net'
    S->>P: Start proxy (real key, forced model,<br/>budget, per-solve token) on random port
    S->>D: Run sandbox container (hardened,<br/>internal net, /work bind mount)
    S->>B: exec harness.py<br/>(inject proxy URL + per-solve token)
    B->>B: Load agent.py, call solve(repo, task, ...)
    loop until solved / budget / timeout
        B->>P: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer = per-solve token
        P->>P: Auth, force model/params,<br/>check + clamp budget
        P->>U: Forward with REAL key injected
        U-->>P: Completion
        P-->>B: Relay response (key never seen)
    end
    B->>B: Compute authoritative git diff
    B-->>S: __TAU_RESULT__ { success, patch, exit_reason }
    S->>P: usage_snapshot() → classify infra vs miner fault
    S->>D: Kill + remove container
    S->>P: Stop proxy
    S->>S: Persist result (or leave for retry if infra fault)
